[[File:AberdeenBestiaryFolio009rPantherDetail.jpg|thumb|right|Folio 9 recto : [[Panther (legendary creature)|Panther]] (''Panther'').]]
[[File:F11v-aberdeen-best-detail.jpg|thumb|right|Folio 11 verso : [[Hyena]] (''Yena'').]]
[[File:F13r-aberdeen-best.jpg|thumb|right|Folio 13 recto : [[Satyr]] (''Satyrs'').]]
[[File:F15r-aberdeen-best-detail.jpg|thumb|right|Folio 15 recto : [[Monocerus|Monoceros]] (''Monoceros'').]]
